data.description: Enjoy small town life in this adorable 2 bedroom 1 bathroom home located in down town Milford. This home features a Large open living room with LVP floors, & wood stove that supplements the gas forced air heat for lower utility bills. Partially fenced backyard with storage shed. Great starter home or investment opportunity with so much potential. HUD home Sold As-Is by electronic bid only. Submit all electronic bids using case #523-107269. HOME SOLD AS-IS. BUYER/BUYER'S AGENT TO VERIFY SQ FT & YEAR BUILT & ALL INFORMATION.
